{"tid":2100232,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"有個鬼佬喺FB撐國安法，仲要過萬followers","createTime":"2020-07-09T01:53:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-09T04:35:09.000Z","uid":38024,"like":37,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"592d6838c1a9dd7658f85af49875531e3d04abc0","tid":2100232,"uid":38024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T01:53:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wrnfuwf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWrnfuwf.png&h=5b69bec5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n幾乎每個po都係屌香港示威者搞亂香港<br />\n仲要有好多留言撐佢 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/nury.vittachi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fnury.vittachi&d=LWtkxptWC%2F4RDCuqQUibmouQyocENDzUuJTHoiHzCac%3D&h=9eb764b6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/nury.vittachi</a><br />\n<br />\n跟手google一下 原來虎報記者嚟<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nury_Vittachi?wprov=sfti1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FNury_Vittachi%3Fwprov%3Dsfti1&d=LWtkxptWC%2F4RDCuqQUibmouQyocENDzUuJTHoiHzCac%3D&h=7df14470\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nury_Vittachi?wprov=sfti1</a><br />\n<br />\n然後又發現咗佢係疑似英籍人士<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Sjb0FEO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSjb0FEO.png&h=5cfab69d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原來英國人都撐我哋國安法呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：愛黨愛國，希望比多啲人知道香港有好多人都撐中國 愛香港嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea7e0f35766bfb0b79b6b7d28502fe7870332a13","tid":2100232,"uid":38024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T01:54:24.000Z","msg":"大家可以入去佢fb留言 表達一下對佢嘅支持"},{"pid":"7aa39c9f7f8dc577f1e68a9d11f8e2a1398f44f2","tid":2100232,"uid":38024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T01:54:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{